Package: trialtracker
Title: Creates a Dashboard for monitoring clinical trial status
Version: 1.9
Authors@R: 
    person("Robert", "Willans", , "robertjwillans@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3461-9691"))
Description: The Trialtracker dashboard is an shinydashboard implementation which monitors clinical trials, displaying basic information on trial status in a dashboard. It also provides email updates when a change in status is detected.
